OL,3,CLife sentence for killer who set fire
OL,4,Cto girlfriend
OL,6,FA man whose girlfriend died two years
OL,7,Fafter he set her on fire has been
OL,8,Fjailed for life for her murder.
OL,10,FLeigh Pateman doused 41-year-old Ellen
OL,11,FMarshall in petrol as she sat in a
OL,12,Fchair during an argument at their home
OL,13,Fin Firbeck Avenue, Skegness, in April
OL,14,F2021, before setting her alight.
OL,16,FPateman, 45, was jailed in March 2022
OL,17,Ffor 17 years and 10 months after he
OL,18,Fadmitted causing the mother-of-four
OL,19,Fgrievous bodily harm with intent.
