OL,6,FBut the Crown Prosecution Service
OL,7,Fbrought a murder charge after Ms
OL,8,FMarshall died aged 43 nearly two years
OL,9,Fafter the attack.
OL,11,FPateman, who pleaded guilty last
OL,12,Fmonth, appeared at Lincoln Crown Court
OL,13,Fon Monday via a video link from HMP
OL,14,FGarth.
OL,16,FWearing a black and white t-shirt, he
OL,17,Fspoke only to confirm his name and
OL,18,Fshowed little emotion as he was
OL,19,Fsentenced to life with a minimum term
OL,20,Fof 27 years, of which he has already
OL,21,Fserved more than three years.
