OL,6,FJudge Hirst told Pateman the attack
OL,7,Fhad been planned and was part of a
OL,8,Fpattern of "terrifying" Ms Marshall in
OL,9,Fthe weeks before it happened.
OL,11,FHe said: "Ms Marshall endured the most
OL,12,Fexcrutiating pain and suffering from
OL,13,Fthe injuries you inflicted upon her."
OL,15,FThe court heard distressing details of
OL,16,Fthe scene which met fire crews who
OL,17,Fwere called to the couple's shared
OL,18,Fhouse in Firbeck Avenue by a neighbour
OL,19,Fat around 10.30pm on 22 April 2021.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/10
