OL,6,FOnce inside, they found the living
OL,7,Froom covered in black smoke. Ms
OL,8,FMarshall, who was originally from
OL,9,FNottingham, was writhing around in
OL,10,F"extreme pain".
OL,12,F"There was little hair left on her
OL,13,Fhead," Prosecutor Sarah Knight said.
OL,14,F"Her face was so badly burnt and
OL,15,Fscorched it was difficult to make out
OL,16,Fher facial features.
OL,18,F"Her body was scorched where her
OL,19,Fclothes would have been."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/10
