OL,6,FMs Marshall managed to give her name
OL,7,Fand age, and initially claimed to have
OL,8,Fcaused the injuries herself.
OL,10,FMiss Knight said it was clear at that
OL,11,Fstage Ms Marshall was still trying to
OL,12,Fprotect Pateman.
OL,14,FOne neighbour described hearing
OL,15,FPateman saying "he had set fire to
OL,16,Fher." Another neighbour heard Ms
OL,17,FMarshall screaming and saw Pateman
OL,18,Fcarrying sauces of water to put on Ms
OL,19,FMarshall.
