OL,6,FPateman was seen cycling away as the
OL,7,Ffire crews arrived.
OL,9,FMs Marshall suffered burns to her
OL,10,Fface, neck, abdomen, chest and limbs,
OL,11,Flost several fingers and sustained
OL,12,Fserious eye injuries in the attack.
OL,14,FShe had suffered 80% burns and was
OL,15,Ftaken to Nottingham City Hospital,
OL,16,Fbefore being transferred to a
OL,17,Fspecialist burns unit.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/10
