OL,6,FHe was arrested and treated for burns
OL,7,Fbefore being taken into police custody.
OL,9,FMiss Knight said Ms Marshall was
OL,10,Frepeatedly re-admitted to the
OL,11,Fspecialist burns unit at Nottingham
OL,12,FCity Hospital and finally died from
OL,13,Fpneumonia on 11 March 2023.
OL,15,FTwo medical experts concluded the
OL,16,Flongstanding burns suffered by Ms
OL,17,FMarshall contributed to her early
OL,18,Fdeath.
OL,20,F"For two years she had that to cope
OL,21,Fwith in her life," Miss Knight added.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/10
