OL,6,FAn impact statement from Ms Marshall's
OL,7,Fdaughter, Paige Clarke, described how
OL,8,Fdespite her burns Ms Marshall kept
OL,9,Ffighting to be a mother to her four
OL,10,Fchildren one day hoped to hold her
OL,11,Ffirst grandchild.
OL,13,FBut Ms Clarke added "that day will now
OL,14,Fnever come."
OL,16,F"She became weaker and weaker as the
OL,17,Fdays went by, but even then she was so
OL,18,Fstrong of heart," Ms Clarke said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/10
