OL,6,F"The physical, mental and emotional
OL,7,Fpain that my mother had to go through
OL,8,Fis almost impossible to put into
OL,9,Fwords," Miss Clarke said.
OL,11,F"She could not bare to look at herself
OL,12,Ffor a year."
